Here’s a dope YouTube video I just dropped on building wealth & creating Family S.O.P’s
•

Family Standard Operating Procedures are the guidelines that easy family should have in place so that the generations that follow have the actual blueprint to sustain wealth.
•

What usually happens is, one generation acquires the wealth through learning the rules to the game & making the investments.
•

Then they usually pass the wealth to the next generation who saw the grind so they may appreciate it.
•

But by the 3rd generation,there’s no ties to the struggle, their entire life is on a silver platter, wealth is normalize, but there’s no blueprint to keep it & no reference point for them to look back on and say this is where we come from.
•

Go check out the full YouTube clip on Family S.O.P’s on my YouTube Channel.
•

Here’s a dope YouTube video I just dropped on building wealth & creating Family S.O.P’s
•

Family Standard Operating Procedures are the guidelines that easy family should have in place so that the generations that follow have the actual blueprint to sustain wealth.
•

What usually happens is, one generation acquires the wealth through learning the rules to the game & making the investments.
•

Then they usually pass the wealth to the next generation who saw the grind so they may appreciate it.
•

But by the 3rd generation,there’s no ties to the struggle, their entire life is on a silver platter, wealth is normalize, but there’s no blueprint to keep it & no reference point for them to look back on and say this is where we come from.
•

Go check out the full YouTube clip on Family S.O.P’s on my YouTube Channel.

And that’s cool, because we all had to learn. I just want us to identify that before we can’t get to the money, we gotta learn. how to break the weed down and put it in the bag first.

Fintech consist of the following:

Payment Processing, Online and mobile banking, Online peer 2 peer lending, Person 2 person payments, financial software & financial services.

Fintech will not replace banks, but it will make traditional banking undergo major adjustments.

node.text:
You’re on your way to work or in bed asking yourself why aren’t you making progress, why isn’t this shit going as planned?
•

You might be even thinking about giving up… NOT ON MY DAMN WATCH!
•

This shit ain’t easier, building wealth ain’t easy, starting and maintaining a successful business ain’t easy but all of it pays off in the end.
•

You gotta stay committed, your job ain’t easy, but you show up everyday whether you’re tired, sick, frustrated no matter what, you push yourself to show up.
•

I Dare You To Show Up Everyday For Your Damn Self Like That.
•

The end Result you want IS POSSIBLE, you just gotta be dedicated to consistency.
•

You’re more dedicated to starting over, stop starting over. This shit don’t get easier, you just get better at pushing through & figuring things out.
•

i need you to comment “ IM COMMITTED” in the comments if you’re no longer starting over, you’re dedicated to the process!
•

I need you to comment “IM COMMITTED” if you’re gonna put that blueprint together & not switch up until you’ve exhausted every possibility you have.
•

I need you to Comment “IM COMMITTED” if you understand that Success & Wealth are your birth right!
•

WALLSTREET LOOKS LIKE US NOW⚖️🏚⚖️🏚
